snippet: Anthony Davis scored 24 points and grabbed eight rebounds to lead the New Orleans Pelicans to an 88-79 victory over the Chicago Bulls on Saturday night....

headline.print_headline: Davis Stays Hot, Lifts Pelicans Over Bulls 88-79
headline.main: Davis Stays Hot, Lifts Pelicans Over Bulls 88-79
